data.description: Magnificent Lindal Cedar Home  meticulously maintained, with lots of vintage charm.  Large Primary bedroom with attached bath. There is also a guest bath Large cozy loft area. Partially finished basement offer endless opportunity  for expansion. Enjoy sunsets, star gazing, or watch the deer go by from the wrap around deck. When the weather gets chilly enjoy those views from the expansive windows in the vaulted great room. Perfect for a family home or as a vacation rental. Property backs up to Forest Service Land,. Seller is offering an additional one acre adjacent lot in this sale.
